<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l7"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nehſt ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> geſant hetten / wol fürbracht vnd geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l8">wıe Jr Jn ſleẅnıgs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> geholffen . vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l9">ın <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> beweıſet habt / ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l10">et <expan>ecıa<ex>m</ex></expan> cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>cluſa</expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
