<ab>Der stat zum <expan>Ellmpog<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns haben die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die wir von des
                            <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Schikenhof<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> gesant hetten, wol fürbracht und gesagt,
                        wie ir in slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> geholffen und
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und guten
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiset habt. Ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> et <expan>ecia<ex>m</ex></expan> cettula
                                <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan> ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
